{"id":538398,"date":[{"year":1974,"month":8,"day":28}],"page":"3","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"","column":"红小兵批林批孔儿歌选,把中小学的批林批孔运动抓紧抓好","genre":"","count":"118","ytitle":"","mtitle":"批林批孔形势好","ftitle":"","authors":["孔仲朝","孔庆衍"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"杨家渡小学儿歌组　孔仲朝　孔庆衍"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"批林批孔形势好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"教室里面真热闹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"口诛笔伐齐参战，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你画画来我写稿。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大批判，坚持搞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"暑假期内劲头高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深入普及又持久，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"批臭孔丘和林彪!"}]}